%N A395262 Triangle read by rows: Expansion of g.f. A(x,y) that satisfies the functional equation A(x,y) = Sum_{j>=0} x^(j*(j+1)/2) * y^j * A(x,y)^j / Product_{k=1..j} (1 - x^k * y * A(x,y)).
